  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Gtk+ 3</title>

    <para>
      The <application>Gtk+ 3</application> package contains
      <application>Gtk+ 3</application> libraries used for creating
      graphical user interfaces for applications.
    </para>

    &lfs71_checked;

